These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, spanish, german
1. the german is on the left of the spanish##1
2. the german is between the polish and the spanish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | polish | german | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, mystery, comedy
1. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | spy | mystery |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, gospel, techno
1. the fan of gospel is between the fan of indie and the fan of techno##2
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | techno | gospel | indie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | hamster | fish | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, water
1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking water and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | iced-tea | water |

 #################################

 
